| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4636 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 37af7b01-022e-5e94-a7b4-f8099db3495f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
